    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by. I'm selling my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable ride that still looks and feels great. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road whenever you are. I'd love for it to go to a good home where it'll be appreciated. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to chat more about it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
